7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"ISO 45001:2015 Certification Mandatory Documents List"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:48+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"List of all ISO 45001:2015 certification mandatory documents list."}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001:2015 Certification Mandatory Documents List"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001:2015 Certification has finally been released, therefore experts and organizations considering a transition or implementation are researching the requirements for recorded information. The new standard takes a fresh look at document and record control, replacing the OHSAS 18001 standards for records and processes with new criteria for documented information. For more details refer the article ISO 45001 Certification Requirements for Companies."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The standard specifies two terms that identify the type of document that is requested. The phrase “retain documented information as proof of...” indicates that the record must be made, but the phrase “maintain as documented information” indicates that the document, including the procedures, must be developed."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The following is a list of the obligatory documented information needed by ISO 45001, as well as the most often utilized papers in the implementation of an Occupational Health and Safety Management System (OH&SMS).You want more details about document structure, read this article ISO 45001 Documentation Structure."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001:2015 requires mandatory documentation and records."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"If you wish to be ISO 45001 compliant, you must create the following documents:"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The OH&S management system's scope"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Occupation Health and Safety Policy"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"OH&SMS OH&S process responsibilities"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Authority for managing risks and opportunities"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Methodology and criteria for assessing occupational health and safety hazards"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Occupational health and safety objectives and plans for achieving them"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Process of emergency preparedness and reaction"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Click here to know the Myths about ISO 45001 OHSMS Certification in Dubai with more detailed information on the most common ways for structuring and implementing mandatory documents and record."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20","$L21","$L22","$L23","$L24","$L25","$L26","$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d","$L2e"]}],"$L2f"]}]}]
