10:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"And here are the records that must be kept:"}]
11:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Occupational health and safety hazards and opportunities, as well as steps to address them"}]
12:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Legal and other prerequisites"}]
13:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Competence evidence"}]
14:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Communication evidence"}]
15:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Preparedness plans for probable emergencies"}]
16:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Monitoring, measurement, analysis, and performance assessment outcomes"}]
17:["$","p","21",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Monitoring equipment maintenance, calibration, or verification"}]
18:["$","p","22",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The outcomes of the compliance evaluation"}]
19:["$","p","23",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Program for internal auditing"}]
1a:["$","p","24",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Report on internal auditing"}]
1b:["$","p","25",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Management review findings"}]
1c:["$","p","26",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The nature of the occurrences or nonconformities, as well as any following action taken"}]
1d:["$","p","27",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The outcomes of any activity, including remedial action, as well as their efficacy"}]
1e:["$","p","28",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Evidence of the outcomes of ongoing progress."}]
1f:["$","p","29",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"You may learn more about the differences between Certification Audit and Surveillance Audit by reading the article \"ISO 14001 Certification Audit vs. Surveillance Audit.\""}]
20:["$","p","30",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Non-Mandatory documents for ISO 45001 Certification in Dubai"}]
21:["$","p","31",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Various non-mandatory publications may be used to implement ISO 45001. However, the following are the most often used non-mandatory documents:"}]
22:["$","p","32",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Procedure for Determining Organizational Context and Interested Parties"}]
23:["$","p","33",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Mandatory Occupational Health and Safety Manual or document"}]
24:["$","p","34",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001 Procedure for Employee Consultation and Participation"}]
25:["$","p","35",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Procedure for Identifying and Assessing Hazards"}]
26:["$","p","36",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Procedure for Determining Legal Requirements"}]
27:["$","p","37",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Communication Procedure"}]
28:["$","p","38",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Control Procedure for Documents and Records"}]
29:["$","p","39",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Operational Planning and Control Procedure"}]
2a:["$","p","40",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Change Management Procedure"}]
2b:["$","p","41",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Monitoring, Measuring, and Analysis Procedure"}]
2c:["$","p","42",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Evaluation of Compliance Procedure"}]
2d:["$","p","43",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To get ISO Certification in UAE, our Wizms experts are ready to help you. Looking at the criteria for documented information in ISO 45001 certification in Abu Dhabi, it is easy to conclude that the same methodology is used as in other management system standards that have changed in recent years. The fundamental goal of the documentation requirements is to guarantee process consistency and give proof that procedures are followed; thus, by satisfying the documentation requirements of the standard, the organization will almost definitely achieve this goal."}]
2e:["$","p","44",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms is the most reputable ISO Certification Consultants in Dubai, UAE, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ras al-Khaimah, Ajman, Al Ain, and Fujairah. To obtain ISO Certification in Dubai we provide excellent ISO training, consulting, implementation, and auditing services for ISO certification. Wizms offers ISO consulting services with a worldwide reach. Our crew is highly skilled and well-versed in the intricacies of the ISO certification process."}]
